@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Login/Inregistrare";
}

<section class="auth-choice-page">
    <h1>Inregistrare si Autentificare</h1>

    <div class="auth-choice-grid">
        <article class="auth-choice-card">
            <div class="auth-choice-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 12a4 4 0 1 0-4-4 4 4 0 0 0 4 4Zm0 2c-3.31 0-6 2.02-6 4.5V21h12v-2.5c0-2.48-2.69-4.5-6-4.5Z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Cont Individual<br />(Persoana Fizica sau Juridica)</h2>
            <div class="auth-choice-card__actions">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-action="LoginForm">Logare cont existent</a>
                <a class="btn btn-dark" asp-action="Register" asp-route-role="Cumparator">Inregistrare cont individual</a>
            </div>
            <p>Acest tip de cont este potrivit pentru utilizatorii care doresc sa cumpere vehicule prin licitatie si sa salveze anunturi favorite.</p>
            <p>Ai acces la licitatii active, istoric de oferte, favorite, notificari si tranzactii castigate.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="auth-choice-card">
            <div class="auth-choice-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M4 4h8a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v12h-2v-2H6v2H4V4Zm2 2v2h2V6H6Zm4 0v2h2V6h-2ZM6 10v2h2v-2H6Zm4 0v2h2v-2h-2Zm6 1h2.2l2.8 3.4V18h-2a2 2 0 1 1-4 0h-5a2 2 0 1 1-4 0H5v-2h11v-5Zm1.5 1.5V15h2.7l-2.1-2.5h-.6Z" />
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h2>Cont Dealer Auto<br />Profesionist</h2>
            <div class="auth-choice-card__actions">
                <a class="btn btn-primary" asp-action="LoginForm">Logare cont existent</a>
                <a class="btn btn-dark" asp-action="Register" asp-route-role="Vanzator">Inregistrare cont dealer auto</a>
            </div>
            <p>Acest cont este conceput pentru vanzatorii care publica vehicule si gestioneaza licitatiile proprii.</p>
            <p>Poti adauga anunturi, administra poze, urmari oferte, primi notificari si gestiona tranzactii finalizate.</p>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>
